OL,3,CHusband and wife jailed for
OL,4,Ctrafficking and prostitution
OL,6,FA husband and wife have been jailed
OL,7,Ffor running a human trafficking and
OL,8,Fprostitution operation in Aldershot.
OL,10,FWei-Gong Li, 45, and Yafeng Dong, 53,
OL,11,Fof Birchett Road, Aldershot, used two
OL,12,Faddresses, one in Aldershot and one in
OL,13,FGuildford, for prostitution and would
OL,14,Ftransport women to the addresses to
OL,15,Fmeet people who paid for sex.
