OL,3,CHusband and wife jailed for
OL,4,Ctrafficking and prostitution
OL,6,FOfficers from the Serious and
OL,7,FOrganised Crime Unit (SOCU) launched
OL,8,Fan investigation following a concern
OL,9,Ffor safety visit at an address in
OL,10,FAscot Court, Aldershot, in November
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FA lone woman was found inside the main
OL,14,Fbedroom, which contained lingerie and
OL,15,Fcondoms.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
