OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773616288
OL,3,CHusband and wife jailed for
OL,4,Ctrafficking and prostitution
OL,6,FOfficers then executed warrants in
OL,7,FAscot Court, Birchett Road and
OL,8,FBellerby Apartments in Guildford and
OL,9,Fseized 12 counterfeit ID documents, 10
OL,10,Fmobile phones, laptops, keys, a USB
OL,11,Fstick, and sim cards.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, financial investigations
OL,14,Funcovered #182,385 in cash deposits
OL,15,Fthat were unaccounted for in terms of
OL,16,Flegitimate income.
OL,18,FMobile phone examinations later
OL,19,Fconfirmed the pair managed the
OL,20,Fbrothels, arranged payments and moved
OL,21,Fwomen between properties.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
