OL,3,CHusband and wife jailed for
OL,4,Ctrafficking and prostitution
OL,6,FThe pair pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fprostitution and exploitation charges.
OL,9,FLi was jailed for two years and one
OL,10,Fmonth, while Dong was jailed for two
OL,11,Fyears and eight months at Winchester
OL,12,FCrown Court on Friday 13 March.
OL,14,FDS Paul Jarrett, from the Serious and
OL,15,FOrganised Crime Unit, said: "Wei-Gong
OL,16,FLi and Yafeng Dong were involved in an
OL,17,Forganised criminal enterprise which
OL,18,Ftargeted and exploited vulnerable
OL,19,Fwomen.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
