OL,3,CHusband and wife jailed for
OL,4,Ctrafficking and prostitution
OL,6,F"The women were controlled and used
OL,7,Ffor sex work purely for the financial
OL,8,Fgain of the couple.
OL,10,F"Our officers take reports of modern
OL,11,Fslavery, human trafficking and
OL,12,Fexploitation extremely seriously and
OL,13,Fwill do everything we can to put those
OL,14,Fresponsible before the courts."
